Underwear tycoon Michelle Mone is selling her three-bedroom Glasgow townhouse in order to buy her ex-husband out of the ` dream home ' they shared .
The self-made multi-millionaire bought the Glasgow property off-plan in the city 's upmarket Park Circus area after splitting from husband Michael .
She will now move back into the five-bedroom mansion in Thorntonhall , Lanarkshire where she and Michael lived with their three children .